divs: Sighting DetailsI weent out to my backyard and looked up to the sky turned to the left and it caught my eye it was kinda transparent but glowed it was moving faster than a plane cause i live close enough to the airport that i can tell and the way it was travelling i mean the speed and the smoothness i knew that this was not a plane it's been cloudy all day but worse tonight cause the wind is up so i saw it glide going toward the south and disappear behind the clouds but what was weird was 2-5 minutes after the f16 jets were deployed i thought this is weird and they were heading in the direction the whatever was going? I don't know? I hope someone saw the same thing.
Summary: went out back looked up and saw orb
